The paper discusses XML data warehouses and their performance issues, which are relevant to the database (cs.DB) and distributed computing (cs.DC) sub-categories. The proposed solution involves fragmentation, which is a common technique in distributed systems (cs.DS). The paper also mentions analytical queries, which are related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and decision-support applications, which are related to software engineering (cs.SE).
